22:59.760 --> 23:00.760
You refuse?

23:00.800 --> 23:01.960
Absolutely.

23:02.000 --> 23:03.640
I refuse
to kiss your feet...

23:06.320 --> 23:09.440
but I will kiss
your lovely hand...

23:10.760 --> 23:12.760
to show trust...

23:12.800 --> 23:15.000
respect...

23:17.480 --> 23:18.520
love.

