29:43.920 --> 29:47.200
You were his favourite,

29:47.240 --> 29:49.600
but you betrayed him.

29:49.640 --> 29:52.560
I didn't betray him.

29:52.600 --> 29:53.840
Pwykka tricked me.

29:53.880 --> 29:55.040
If Lokka is here,

29:55.080 --> 29:56.360
Pwykka won't be
far behind...

29:58.720 --> 30:01.880
and the age of Wonder
is at an end.

30:09.360 --> 30:11.120
Are you
looking for someone?

30:13.440 --> 30:15.840
I seek the mighty Veran.

30:15.880 --> 30:17.920
I'll do whatever he wants.

30:17.960 --> 30:20.360
I'm ready.

30:20.400 --> 30:21.640
Are you sure?

30:22.680 --> 30:26.120
You heard me, you ugly bitch.

30:26.160 --> 30:28.360
I'm ready!

30:28.400 --> 30:30.320
Then come inside.

30:57.960 --> 30:59.480
Follow me, child.

31:03.600 --> 31:05.760
Where is he?

31:05.800 --> 31:09.960
First we must discover
how ready you are.

31:10.000 --> 31:13.200
I am ready.

31:18.000 --> 31:21.040
I am ready.

31:53.360 --> 31:54.840
Sit.

32:08.400 --> 32:10.600
What do you see
when you look at me?

32:12.920 --> 32:16.320
When I look at you,
I see darkness...

32:16.360 --> 32:19.520
darkness and lies.

32:19.560 --> 32:20.560
So I'm a liar?

32:22.760 --> 32:25.120
I know Rome came to you.

32:25.160 --> 32:26.080
They made a deal.

32:28.000 --> 32:29.480
They knew they couldn't
deal with my father,

32:29.520 --> 32:30.520
so you did
their bidding.

32:32.880 --> 32:34.920
You killed my father

32:34.960 --> 32:37.240
not because
the gods told you to,

32:37.280 --> 32:38.720
but to save
yourself.

32:38.760 --> 32:43.160
Many think they can influence
the ruling of the gods.

32:43.200 --> 32:46.000
The gods' voice is the wind...

32:46.040 --> 32:47.520
the earthquake...

32:47.560 --> 32:48.600
the famine.

32:48.640 --> 32:50.320
But you're not the wind.

32:52.480 --> 32:53.480
You're human.

32:57.920 --> 32:59.880
What's the difference?

33:10.800 --> 33:14.880
There is something
I need to tell you.

33:14.920 --> 33:16.920
The Roman General
came here.

33:16.960 --> 33:17.880
When?

33:17.920 --> 33:19.920
Soon after the
Romans landed,

33:19.960 --> 33:21.960
and Veran...

33:22.000 --> 33:25.280
took him
to the Underworld.

33:25.320 --> 33:26.400
No, no, no, no.

33:27.400 --> 33:30.040
If he risked
travelling to the Underworld,

33:30.080 --> 33:31.960
to walk among our dead,

33:32.000 --> 33:34.160
then...

33:36.120 --> 33:38.160
he went
to find something important.

33:38.200 --> 33:39.600
Follow his footsteps.

33:39.640 --> 33:42.640
Only then will you know
what it is he seeks...

33:45.440 --> 33:46.680
and what might save us.

34:19.480 --> 34:22.880
Romans are demons...

34:22.920 --> 34:26.000
foot soldiers for
the great Earth Demon Lokka.

34:26.040 --> 34:27.239
They come in disguise,

34:27.280 --> 34:31.159
pretending to bring
protection, bounty,

34:31.199 --> 34:34.280
but in truth, they bring
only chaos and destruction.

34:34.320 --> 34:37.560
Yes, Rome came to me,

34:37.600 --> 34:38.880
and I listened.

34:38.920 --> 34:42.560
They thought
you would be wiser,

34:42.600 --> 34:44.719
asked me
to sacrifice your father

34:44.760 --> 34:46.040
and replace him
with you.

34:46.080 --> 34:47.679
And that's exactly
what you did.

34:47.719 --> 34:48.800
Indeed...

34:48.840 --> 34:52.560
but that's not
why your father is gone.

34:54.239 --> 34:55.080
Then why?

34:56.960 --> 34:58.440
This day,

34:58.480 --> 35:00.800
Lokka believes the Druids
have done his bidding,

35:00.840 --> 35:03.600
but Lokka is wrong.

35:03.640 --> 35:07.600
The gods would not choose you
for such a reason,

35:07.640 --> 35:09.760
for the gods cannot be bought.

35:11.320 --> 35:12.800
The gods chose you

35:12.840 --> 35:13.960
because the gods know

35:14.000 --> 35:16.800
you are strong enough
to defeat Lokka,

35:16.840 --> 35:18.520
and to do that,

35:18.560 --> 35:21.680
you have to be prepared
to sacrifice everything.

35:40.720 --> 35:41.720
What did he say?

35:46.600 --> 35:48.120
Kerra...

35:48.160 --> 35:49.400
what did he
say to you?

35:49.440 --> 35:51.960
Have you decided?

35:52.000 --> 35:53.520
I have.

35:53.560 --> 35:54.800
So?

35:57.600 --> 36:00.440
I will become Queen.

36:00.480 --> 36:03.320
I will rule my people.

38:57.120 --> 39:00.160
Before the gods, there was
nothing but chaos.

39:00.200 --> 39:04.840
Now we stand held
under their unyielding gaze...

39:04.880 --> 39:08.800
below the cold moon,
beneath the stars.

39:14.280 --> 39:15.520
I have one question.

39:23.960 --> 39:26.960
Did your general
ever meet with the Druids?

39:30.240 --> 39:31.600
Child of the Night...

39:32.560 --> 39:36.280
Sword of the Gods, I crown you.

39:36.320 --> 39:40.680
May you never speak again,
except to show us the way.

39:42.960 --> 39:45.400
Do you feel
the gods' pleasure?

39:45.440 --> 39:46.840
I do.

39:48.400 --> 39:50.640
Then rise up,
Queen Kerra.

39:58.240 --> 40:00.880
Queen Kerra.

40:01.920 --> 40:03.040
Queen Kerra.

40:10.000 --> 40:12.640
Get your stuff.
We're leaving.

40:35.600 --> 40:37.920
It's a mistake.

40:39.200 --> 40:42.800
Then it's my mistake.

40:42.840 --> 40:45.000
I've made plenty of others.

40:46.120 --> 40:49.440
You must go
to Amena now.

40:49.480 --> 40:51.280
She needs you.

40:54.960 --> 40:57.640
I'm sorry, Lindon.

40:57.680 --> 40:58.880
This is the gods' will.

40:58.920 --> 41:01.080
What has he done to you?

41:01.120 --> 41:03.400
This is what
the Druids decreed.

41:03.440 --> 41:06.000
Listen to yourself.

41:06.040 --> 41:07.720
You walk into that circle
as one thing,

41:07.760 --> 41:08.720
and you return saying this?

41:08.760 --> 41:11.840
You will do as I command.

41:53.400 --> 41:55.440
The night
they took my mother away,

41:55.480 --> 41:57.760
you wrote something.

41:57.800 --> 41:59.640
Here.

42:01.760 --> 42:03.120
What does it say?

42:03.160 --> 42:05.600
Those words are from the gods.

42:07.640 --> 42:09.600
Not until the day
you leave this world

42:09.640 --> 42:10.800
can they be read.

42:10.840 --> 42:11.840
Read them to me.

42:14.160 --> 42:17.040
If I am to trust you...

42:17.080 --> 42:18.240
I need to know.

42:18.280 --> 42:19.400
Trust is
not important.

42:19.440 --> 42:21.080
Only faith.

42:26.600 --> 42:29.160
If I am
the Sword of the Gods,

42:29.200 --> 42:30.760
you will read me the runes.

42:33.400 --> 42:35.360
How will you know
I'm telling you the truth?

42:38.000 --> 42:39.960
I'll know.

42:53.920 --> 42:55.800
These words...
they say,

42:55.840 --> 42:59.120
"Hope is the daughter
of a blind father."

43:33.920 --> 43:35.760
Here, father.

43:38.200 --> 43:40.280
Thank you,
my child.

